                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen-doped coal gas mixed fuel heating furnace low-carbon combustion system and control method",
                    "一种掺氢煤气混合燃料的加热炉低碳燃烧系统及控制方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of metallurgical industry furnace energy-saving combustion, in particular to a heating furnace low-carbon combustion system of hydrogen-doped gas mixed fuel and a control method. Comprising a heating furnace, an air pipeline, a gas pipeline and a hydrogen pipeline which are connected with the heating furnace, and preheaters of the gas pipelines. An on-line calorific value meter is arranged on a pipeline where coal gas is preheated, an electronic flow valve is arranged on each pipeline, an electronic flow valve is arranged on a pipeline between an outlet of each preheater and each burner of the heating furnace, and the heating furnace can detect the calorific value of the coal gas in real time. The flow of coal gas and hydrogen is adjusted in real time according to production temperature requirements, so that the temperature in the heating furnace is kept stable, and carbon emission of the heating furnace is reduced; according to the control method, the temperature stability in the heating furnace can be improved, control is flexible, and carbon emission of the heating furnace can be effectively reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及冶金工业炉窑节能燃烧技术领域，具体涉及一种掺氢煤气混合燃料的加热炉低碳燃烧系统及控制方法。包括加热炉，与加热炉相连接的空气管路、煤气管路和氢气管路，以及各气体管路的预热器。煤气在预热前的管路上设置有在线热值仪，且在每一个管路上分别设置电子流量阀，每个预热器的出口与加热炉各烧嘴之间的管路也设置有电子流量阀，所述的加热炉可以通过实时检测煤气热值，根据生产温度需求实时调整煤气和氢气的流量，使加热炉内部保持温度稳定，且降低了加热炉的碳排放；本发明的控制方法能够提高加热炉内的温度稳定性，且控制灵活，能够有效降低加热炉的碳排放。"
                }
            ]
